Package edu.cmu.cs.lane.datatypes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CGEModel
    CGEModel represents a model generated by an Analyzer that contains coefficient information for every non-zero coefficient for each genetic (or other) feature.
    CGEModelFeatureBean
    CGEModelFeatureBean represents a result (coefficient) of a model calculation on a specific feature for a specific response variable.
    CGEPrediction
    The CGEPrediction class represents predictions collection that was done for a specific sample (represented by a unique sampleId) using a specific model (represented by a model id)
    CGEPredictionBean
    The CGEPredictionBean class represents a prediction for a specific a patient and model and for a specific clinical variable or clinical state.
    DataSetType  
    SampleGeneticBean
    The class SampleGeneticBean represents (genetic) information of a specific patient.
    SampleLabelBean
    The class SampleLabelBean represents for each sample a hash of clinical variables or sample labels (.e.g., disease state).
    SamplesGeneticData
    The SamplesGeneticData class represents genetic data of one or more samples (patients).
    SamplesLabels
    SamplesLabels is the base class that represents the clinical variables or sample labels (.e.g., disease state).
    SNProwDataBean
